## 🚀 사용 예제

### 1. 하드웨어 연동
```javascript
import { QuantumHardwareInterface } from './quantum-hardware-adapter.js';

const hardware = new QuantumHardwareInterface('ibm');
await hardware.connect();

const circuit = {
  gates: [
    { gate: 'H', qubits: [0] },
    { gate: 'CNOT', qubits: [0, 1] }
  ]
};

const jobInfo = await hardware.submitCircuit(circuit);
const results = await hardware.getResults(jobInfo.jobId);
console.log(results);
```

### 2. 노이즈 모델링
```javascript
import { IntegratedNoiseModel } from './noise-model.js';

const noiseModel = new IntegratedNoiseModel({
  T1: 100,        // 마이크로초
  T2: 50,         // 마이크로초
  singleQubitErrorRate: 0.001,
  temperature: 0.01
});

const noisyCounts = noiseModel.applyCompleteNoise(circuit, counts);
```

### 3. 회로 변환
```javascript
import { CircuitTranspiler } from './circuit-transpiler.js';

const transpiler = new CircuitTranspiler('ibm');
const result = transpiler.transpile(circuit);

console.log(`Optimized gates: ${result.totalGates}`);
console.log(`Circuit depth: ${result.depth}`);
```

### 4. 작업 관리
```javascript
import { JobManager } from './job-manager.js';

const manager = new JobManager({ concurrency: 2 });

manager.submitJob(circuit, { priority: 8, shots: 1000 });
manager.submitJob(circuit, { priority: 5, shots: 1000 });

const results = await manager.processJobs();
```

### 5. 하드웨어 캘리브레이션
```javascript
import { CalibrationEngine } from './calibration-engine.js';

const engine = new CalibrationEngine();
const calibResults = await engine.runFullCalibration();

console.log(`H gate timing: ${calibResults.H.timing.toFixed(2)} ns`);
console.log(`RX optimal amplitude: ${calibResults.RX.optimalAmplitude}`);
```

